{"tid":1385470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（建議）設立提供即時資訊嘅電臺","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T16:39:14.000Z","uid":144497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0ddef9a116d25759208d86ccbc595a06dbdb2b","tid":1385470,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:43:46.000Z","msg":"香港人應要好好<span style=\"color: red;\">利用</span>自己地方<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊流通速度同自由</span><br />\n令<span style=\"color: red;\">即時資訊更加快傳到夢遊人士</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夢遊人士夢遊嗰陣根本<span style=\"color: green;\">無可能即時睇到文字資訊</span><br />\n搵一小部分夢遊人士做資訊傳達會<span style=\"color: green;\">拖慢咗資訊傳送速度</span><br />\n噉咪大家一齊用耳仔聽囉<br />\n淨係戴一隻，另一隻繼續聽周圍環境<br />\n<br />\n夢遊人士遊下遊下，電臺送到料，耳仔收到料<br />\n就可以即刻用心靈感應同其他夢遊人士交流下要點發落去<br />\n<br />\n而電臺有好多種形式，無線電、網絡、數碼乜乜乜<br />\n可以討論邊種電臺係<span style=\"color: gold;\">最容易設立或者最有效率</span>"},{"pid":"f029807b656d6ac3efbb78a6bdda558dbad5ba10","tid":1385470,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:47:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6c46939c6827bff233138a85110a13ae343d29c","tid":1385470,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"070af73e4f8675e31f7686e55b23ef5622d4bb15","tid":1385470,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"成功既話可以救到更多人"},{"pid":"a4ddceb31ffbc61e82fedceb049654fcb5205e2f","tid":1385470,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"060939b9f3fda7a616e655c9b9431c406197c9a3","tid":1385470,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:27:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3703c493d23a43910edae5f69ed9a1fbff29966f","tid":1385470,"uid":144497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:38:53.000Z","msg":"我諗緊電臺有<span style=\"color: 